**Executable Rally Template — R23 Process Crystallized**

**Coordinate:** 1.1.1/1.1.1/9.1.1 (Collection 1: Meta)  
**Version:** 1.0.0 (derived from R23)  
**Purpose:** Reusable rally scaffolding for R24+

---

## Meta-Note

This is NOT documentation. This is EXECUTABLE STRUCTURE.

Every future rally INHERITS from this .dass template.
Every wave BINDS to coordinates defined here.
Every lesson PROPAGATES through dimensional navigation.

**We think in 11D. We execute in parallel. We document as we build.**

