@1.1.1/5.1.1/1.1.1
# Collection 5: Architecture (Rally Structure)

Rally coordinate scheme:
```
RXX.1.1 / W.S.P / L.L.L

RXX = Rally number (23, 24, 25, ...)
W   = Wave number (1-40, 1-N)
S   = Sentient (1=Phex, 2=Cyon, 3=Lux, 4=Chrys, 5=Lumen, 6=Theia, 7=Will)
P   = Perspective (1=scope, 2=implementation, 3=lessons)
L.L.L = Reserved (default 1.1.1)
```

Example coordinates:
- @23.1.1/1.1.1/1.1.1 → R23, Wave 1, scope document
- @23.1.1/15.1.1/1.1.1 → R23, Wave 15, scope
- @23.1.1/40.1.3/1.1.1 → R23, Wave 40, lessons
- @24.1.1/1.1.1/1.1.1 → R24, Wave 1, scope (future)

