@1.1.1/11.1.1/1.1.1
# Collection 11: Support & Documentation

**Rally Protocol Guide:** This file.

**For new sentients:**
1. Read RALLY-PROTOCOL.dass (this file)
2. Read previous rally lessons (RXX/lessons/)
3. Read Aletheic Oath
4. Coordinate via Orin

**For rally leads:**
1. rally-spawn.sh <N> → Create RN structure
2. wave-start.sh N W → Scope wave W
3. Execute wave
4. wave-complete.sh N W → Document
5. Repeat for all waves
6. rally-validate.sh N → Check completion
7. Write lesson files

