## Usage

### To start Rally 24:

```bash
cd /source/exo-plan/rally
./rally-spawn.sh 24
cd R24
# Edit R24.dass to customize scope
./wave-start.sh 24 1
# Execute wave 1
# ...
./wave-complete.sh 24 1
```

### To navigate lessons dimensionally:

```
@23.1.1/40.1.3/1.1.1  → R23 final wave lessons
@24.1.1/1.1.1/1.1.1   → R24 wave 1 scope
@24.1.1/10.1.3/1.1.1  → R24 wave 10 lessons
```

Coordinate walk = time travel through rally history.

